<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 03:15:35 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国恒大子公司交易提高了离岸债权人的前景</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-evergrande-subsidiary-dealings-raises-prospects-offshore-creditors-2024-08-22/</link><description>专家表示，如果中国恒大的境外债权人能够证明该房地产开发商是来自境内子公司的应付款，他们因此有权获得这笔资金，那么他们可能会增加收回资金的机会。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 02:56:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-evergrande-subsidiary-dealings-raises-prospects-offshore-creditors-2024-08-22/</guid></item><item><title>美联储准备降息，股市上涨，美元下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-22/</link><description>周四，亚洲股市小幅走高，而美元兑英镑和欧元则跌至一年低点，因美联储会议纪要显示政策制定者准备开始降息。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 02:11:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-22/</guid></item><item><title>巴西收紧入境规则以遏制移民到北美</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/brazil-tighten-entry-rules-curb-migration-north-america-2024-08-22/</link><description>巴西政府周三表示，在移民越来越多地利用这个南美国家作为前往美国和加拿大途中的中转站之后，巴西将从下周开始收紧免签证入境的规定。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 02:04:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/brazil-tighten-entry-rules-curb-migration-north-america-2024-08-22/</guid></item><item><title>杰克逊霍尔事件前美联储鸽派基调加剧美元低迷</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-doldrums-deepen-dovish-fed-tone-before-jackson-hole-2024-08-22/</link><description>周四，美元兑欧元和英镑汇率接近一年多以来的最低水平，因为鸽派的美联储和美国就业市场疲软的新迹象支持了降息的理由。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 00:46:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-doldrums-deepen-dovish-fed-tone-before-jackson-hole-2024-08-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国佳兆业预计上半年净亏损将因房地产交付放缓而扩大</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-kaisa-forecasts-bigger-h1-net-loss-slower-property-deliveries-2024-08-21/</link><description>中国房地产开发商佳兆业集团周四表示，由于房地产交付量下降和项目减值拨备增加，预计今年上半年将出现更大的净亏损。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 23:47:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-kaisa-forecasts-bigger-h1-net-loss-slower-property-deliveries-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国新的城镇化进程可能会阻碍“生育友好型社会”的目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-fresh-urbanisation-push-may-thwart-birth-friendly-society-goal-2024-08-21/</link><description>孟玛丽在上海一家中国科技公司工作，工作非常忙碌，压力也很大，她无法想象要生第二个孩子。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 23:06:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-fresh-urbanisation-push-may-thwart-birth-friendly-society-goal-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>美国高级官员在纽约会见达赖喇嘛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/senior-us-officials-meet-with-dalai-lama-new-york-2024-08-21/</link><description>美国国务院表示，美国国务院和白宫高级官员周三在纽约会见了达赖喇嘛，并“重申了美国对促进西藏人权的承诺”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 23:03:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/senior-us-officials-meet-with-dalai-lama-new-york-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：韩国央行关注美国国债收益率下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-21/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 21:50:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>美国司法部称，纽约男子被指控监视中国持不同政见者</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/new-york-man-charged-with-acting-chinese-agent-doj-says-2024-08-21/</link><description>美国司法部表示，周三，一名纽约男子被指控作为中国政府在美国的非法代理人，指控他对中国亲民主活动人士和异见人士进行间谍活动。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 21:49:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/new-york-man-charged-with-acting-chinese-agent-doj-says-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>佩纳表示，尽管与台湾有联系，巴拉圭仍通过南方共同市场向中国开放贸易协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/paraguay-open-china-trade-deals-via-mercosur-despite-taiwan-ties-pena-says-2024-08-21/</link><description>巴拉圭总统圣地亚哥·佩纳周三表示，尽管巴拉圭与台湾有外交关系，但他对通过南美贸易集团南方共同市场与中国达成贸易协议“完全开放”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 21:10:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/paraguay-open-china-trade-deals-via-mercosur-despite-taiwan-ties-pena-says-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>据英国《金融时报》报道，普华永道因恒大审计而在中国面临 6 个月的禁令</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/pwc-braces-6-month-ban-china-over-evergrande-audit-ft-reports-2024-08-21/</link><description>据英国《金融时报》周三报道，普华永道中国已通知其客户，预计中国当局最早将于 9 月实施为期六个月的业务禁令，作为对倒闭的房地产开发商恒大集团审计的惩罚的一部分。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 20:13:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/pwc-braces-6-month-ban-china-over-evergrande-audit-ft-reports-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪计划为墨西哥工厂提供国家激励措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-electric-carmaker-byd-unveils-new-plug-in-hybrid-suv-mexico-2024-08-21/</link><description>中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪国家负责人周三表示，该公司已将墨西哥制造厂选址的最终候选名单缩减至三个州，并正在审查这些州提出的一系列激励措施。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 19:09:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-electric-carmaker-byd-unveils-new-plug-in-hybrid-suv-mexico-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>监管机构称中国央行对长期债券发出警告旨在遏制系统性风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-central-bank-warnings-long-dated-bonds-aim-curb-systemic-risks-watchdog-2024-08-21/</link><description>金融市场协会的一位高级官员表示，中国央行对长期主权债券风险敞口过高发出警告，旨在遏制收益率继续下跌时潜在的系统性风险。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 17:54:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-central-bank-warnings-long-dated-bonds-aim-curb-systemic-risks-watchdog-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>摩根士丹利将墨西哥股票下调至“减持”，并下调中国目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/morgan-stanley-cuts-mexico-stocks-underweight-trims-china-targets-2024-08-21/</link><description>出于对司法和选举制度计划改革的担忧，投资银行摩根士丹利周三对墨西哥股市发出“减持”警告，并下调了对中国主要市场的预测。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 13:12:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/morgan-stanley-cuts-mexico-stocks-underweight-trims-china-targets-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>智库警告称，世界大国的战略竞争可能压倒太平洋岛屿</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/world-powers-strategic-rivalry-threatens-overwhelm-pacific-islands-think-tank-2024-08-21/</link><description>一份智库报告在一年一度的太平洋岛屿领导人峰会之前警告称，在中国和美国盟友之间的战略竞争中，地缘政治冲击可能会扰乱政治和安全格局，并导致太平洋岛屿地区的团结紧张。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 12:37:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/world-powers-strategic-rivalry-threatens-overwhelm-pacific-islands-think-tank-2024-08-21/</guid></item></channel></rss>